# âœ“ Enable HTTPS (FORCE_HTTPS=true)
# âœ“ Configure monitoring and error tracking
# âœ“ Set up database backups
#
# TESTING ENVIRONMENT (.env.test):
# âœ“ Use separate test database (barberpro_test)
# âœ“ Mock all external services
# âœ“ Use fast startup (minimal health check retries)
# âœ“ Isolated from dev/prod data
#
